Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.68,0:22:51.47,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H000000&\3a&H80&\bord1\blur5}只是一句话就让我脸红心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.81,0:22:54.60,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H000000&\3a&H80&\bord1\blur5}心中萌生小小情愫
